<p>Lunch and transportation are provided. Snacks and Water would be great to bring for during and after the activity.</p>
<p>Other required tools you'll need:</p>
<ul>
<li>eye protection (safety glasses, or sun glasses)</li>
<li>tools ( hammer, spray bottle, and garden claw)</li>
<li>and good shoes (open toed shoes, flip-flops and sandals will NOT be allowed)</li>
<li>Your fee allows you to bring home 1lb of opal aggragate</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
